    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been garage-kept and pampered since the day I got it\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There isn't a single blemish on it, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to message me if you want to come take a look!",
