    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous coat that remains entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the alloy wheels are immaculate, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin retains its original integrity; the leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service record from certified specialists and an engine bay that is spotless. This is a time-capsule example for the enthusiast who demands perfection and refuses to settle for anything less.",
      "price": 48500.0,
