    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s finally time for someone else to get behind the wheel! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it basically still has that 'new car' smell and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and meticulously detailed. It runs like a total dream and is ready for a new home. You\u2019ve really got to see it in person to believe how pristine it is! Feel free to reach out if you want to chat or come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
