    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a museum-grade example of the A80 platform, preserved in factory-original condition. Under the hood, the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six features sequential twin-turbochargers that deliver a seamless torque curve and robust forced induction performance. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a double-wishbone suspension setup that retains its original geometry. Finished in flawless paint with a pristine interior featuring unmarred leather bolsters and functional analog instrumentation, this specimen represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. Documented service history confirms its mechanical integrity.",
